---
title: Gochujang Glazed Chicken Rice Bowl with Carrot & Spring Onion 'Kimchi' and Peanuts
description: This vibrant Gochujang Glazed Chicken Rice Bowl is sure to put a pep in your step! A cheat's version of the classic Korean side dish kimchi gives plenty of colour as well as delicious flavour.
